{%- comment -%}
  Ganguram zone-visibility config (Phase 2.5).

  Builds window.GanguramZoneKolkataOnly: the handles of collections that have NO
  PAN-India product (i.e. only Kolkata / Quick-Commerce eligible) — derived live
  from each collection's all_tags, so there is NO hardcoded category list and NO
  pincode list duplicated. The menu-visibility engine hides links to these
  collections for PAN-India customers (reversibly).

  Display-only. No cart/checkout/ShipZip/SBZ/zipLogic logic.
{%- endcomment -%}
<script>
  window.GanguramZoneKolkataOnly = [
    {%- for collection in collections limit: 250 -%}
      {%- unless collection.all_tags contains 'PAN India' -%}
        {%- if collection.all_tags contains 'Kolkata' or collection.all_tags contains 'Quick Commerce' -%}
          {{ collection.handle | json }},
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endunless -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
  ];
</script>
{{ 'ganguram-zone-visibility.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
<script src="{{ 'ganguram-zone-visibility.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
